WEBVTT

00:01.200 --> 00:01.791
PREVIOUSLY ON "SALEM"...

00:02.900 --> 00:04.390
Mercy: WITCH!

00:04.430 --> 00:07.797
Emily: NO WOMAN IN SALEM
HAS EVER HAD THAT KIND OF POWER.

00:07.840 --> 00:09.307
Dollie: NOT EVEN MARY SIBLEY.

00:09.340 --> 00:11.558
Tituba:
THE LADY OF THE HOUSE IS MINE.

00:11.610 --> 00:13.999
Increase:
WE'VE UNCOVERED A WITCH.

00:14.040 --> 00:17.077
Mary: HOW LONG MAY WE ENJOY
YOUR CURATIVE PRESENCE IN TOWN?

00:17.110 --> 00:22.719
Increase:
UNTIL EVERY LAST DEVIL'S WHORE
OF A WITCH IN SALEM IS DEAD.

00:22.750 --> 00:24.843
Tituba: PETRUS' PHYSIC
WILL LAST BUT A DAY,

00:24.890 --> 00:27.688
AND THEN MR. SIBLEY WILL AWAKE,
LUCID AND EAGER.

00:27.720 --> 00:29.950
Mary:
TO TELL INCREASE EVERYTHING.

00:36.470 --> 00:39.439
[ ROOSTER CROWS ]

00:48.240 --> 00:49.172
[THUD]

00:49.210 --> 00:50.768
Henry: [ GASPS ]

00:53.550 --> 00:55.211
Increase: CHOOSE ONE.

00:59.220 --> 01:00.414
DRINK.

01:00.460 --> 01:02.849
DRINK AND...ENJOY.

01:02.890 --> 01:07.452
ONLY MERE MORTALS ARE VULNERABLE
TO MANMADE SPIRITS.

01:07.500 --> 01:10.060
AS A MAN,
YOU ARE AN ABOMINATION,

01:10.100 --> 01:13.365
BUT YOU ARE NO WITCH.

01:13.400 --> 01:19.009
NOW BEGONE WITH YOU
AND YOUR. ..PITIFUL WEAKN ESS.

01:25.410 --> 01:29.744
TIME TO WAKE, MY GOOD MADAM.

01:29.790 --> 01:30.814
[ CLANKS ]

01:55.540 --> 02:00.318
LET THEM NO MORE SAY,
"GOD MUST DO ALL,"

02:00.350 --> 02:02.910
AND SO ENCOURAGE THEMSELVES

02:02.950 --> 02:09.628
TO LIVE IN A CARELESS NEGLECT
OF GOD AND OF THEIR OWN SOULS

02:09.660 --> 02:12.197
AND SALVATION!

02:12.230 --> 02:18.965
THE DEVIL HAS MADE A DREADFUL
KNOT OF WITCHES IN THE COUNTRY,

02:19.000 --> 02:20.991
AND, BY THE HELP OF WITCHES,

02:21.040 --> 02:25.500
HAS DREADFULLY INCREASED
THAT KNOT.

02:31.710 --> 02:36.318
OH, CHILDREN,
CHILDREN, BE AFRAID

02:36.350 --> 02:40.980
AND GO NOT PRAYERLESS
TO YOUR BED

02:41.020 --> 02:44.148
LEST THE DEVIL
BE YOUR BEDFELLOW.

02:56.540 --> 02:58.531
[ ROPE CREAKS ]

03:13.460 --> 03:15.519
[ ALL GASP ]

03:21.260 --> 03:22.898
[ "CUPID CARRIES A GUN" PLAYS ]

03:28.900 --> 03:31.607
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

03:31.640 --> 03:33.198
* WITCH DRUMS

03:33.240 --> 03:36.641
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

03:37.550 --> 03:39.711
* POUND ME THE WITCH DRUMS

03:39.750 --> 03:41.115
* THE WITCH DRUMS

03:41.150 --> 03:43.710
* BETTER PRAY FOR HELL

03:43.750 --> 03:49.052
* NOT HALLELUJAH

04:11.950 --> 04:14.145
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

04:19.920 --> 04:21.114
Mary:
GOOD MORNING, REVEREND.

04:21.160 --> 04:22.821
Increase: AH.

04:22.860 --> 04:25.078
MRS. SIBLEY.

04:25.130 --> 04:26.722
[ CHUCKLES ]

04:26.760 --> 04:28.022
JOIN ME.

04:34.700 --> 04:36.065
Mary: THERE ARE NO WORDS

04:36.100 --> 04:38.159
TO ENCOMPASS
MY OVERWHELMING GRATITUDE

04:38.210 --> 04:40.235
AT YOUR RECLAMATION
OF MY HUSBAND.

04:40.280 --> 04:41.804
WHEN I THINK WHAT MIGHT
HAVE TRANSPIRED

04:41.840 --> 04:43.603
HAD YOU NOT BEEN THERE --
-Increase: INDEED?

04:43.650 --> 04:46.107
EXACTLY WHAT MIGHT
HAVE TRANSPIRED?

04:46.150 --> 04:47.913
-Mary: EXCUSE ME?
-Increase: WELL...

04:47.950 --> 04:51.841
WOULD NOT YOUR SLAVE GIRL SIMPLY
HAVE TAKEN HIM ON TO HOSPITAL?

04:51.890 --> 04:53.517
Mary: YES.

04:53.560 --> 04:56.154
Increase: YES, IT WAS YOU
WHO SENT HER TO HIS RESCUE,

04:56.190 --> 04:57.521
WAS IT NOT?

04:57.560 --> 04:58.652
Mary:
ONCE I'D HEARD OF THE ACCIDENT.

04:58.690 --> 05:00.191
Increase: AH.

05:02.200 --> 05:03.963
I AM PERPLEXED, THOUGH.

05:04.000 --> 05:08.630
TELL ME, WHY WAS GEORGE SCURRIED
OFF WITH SUCH HASTE AND SECRECY?

05:08.670 --> 05:11.969
Mary:
HE GOES OFTEN TO BOSTON.

05:12.010 --> 05:14.478
-HIS ILLNESS --
-Increase: HE'S NOT ILL.

05:14.510 --> 05:17.343
HE'S SPELLED.
-Mary: NO.

05:17.380 --> 05:18.642
THAT'S IMPOSSIBLE.

05:18.680 --> 05:20.147
Increase: CONSIDER --

05:20.180 --> 05:24.446
HAS NOT GEORGE SUFFERED
THIS MYSTERIOUS MALADY

05:24.490 --> 05:27.550
WITHOUT EXPLICATION
FOR SEVERAL YEARS NOW,

05:27.590 --> 05:31.185
AND HAVE NOT THE DOCTORS
EXPRESSED UTI'ER BEFUDDLEMENT

05:31.230 --> 05:32.629
AS TO ITS CAUSE?

05:32.660 --> 05:33.558
-Mary: YES, BUT --
-Increase: YES.

05:33.600 --> 05:35.454
IN SUCH CASES,

05:35.500 --> 05:37.661
THE ANSWER
IS OFF THE SIMPLEST ONE.

05:37.700 --> 05:39.634
GEORGE IS NOT ILL.

05:39.670 --> 05:42.833
HE IS UNDER THE INFLUENCE
OF THE DEVIL'S DARKEST TOOL --

05:42.870 --> 05:44.861
A WITCH'S SPELL.

05:44.910 --> 05:49.700
AND IT IS QUITE LIKELY THAT THIS
SPELLER RESIDES CLOSE AT HEARTH.

05:49.750 --> 05:52.002
Mary: NO.

05:52.050 --> 05:56.749
Increase: PERHAPS EVEN IN THE
HALLOWED HALLS OF YOUR OWN HOME.

05:59.020 --> 06:00.385
Mary: SAY IT.

06:00.420 --> 06:01.853
Increase: SAY WHAT?

06:01.890 --> 06:04.085
Mary: THE ACCUSATION.

06:04.130 --> 06:06.086
IT DANCES ON YOUR TONGUE.

06:06.130 --> 06:08.257
Increase: WELL, I ASSURE YOU,
YOU ARE MISTAKEN.

06:08.300 --> 06:09.562
HM.

06:15.070 --> 06:17.937
Mary: THEN I WISH TO BRING
MY HUSBAND HOME IMMEDIATELY.

06:17.970 --> 06:19.574
Increase:
I THINK NOT, MRS. SIBLEY.

06:19.610 --> 06:21.009
Mary:
YOU WOULD DENY ME THAT RIGHT?

06:21.040 --> 06:22.405
Increase:
I MUST DENY YOU THAT RIGHT

06:22.450 --> 06:25.840
UNTIL WE CAN DISCOVER
THE ORIGIN OF THE SPELL.

06:25.880 --> 06:27.916
HMM?

06:30.720 --> 06:33.883
Mary: THEN I WOULD ASK,
OR, RATHER, INSIST,

06:33.920 --> 06:36.718
THAT SOMEONE ATI'END
TO MR. SIBLEY.

06:36.760 --> 06:39.558
SOMEONE WHO HAS EXPERIENCE
WITH HIS TRAVAILS.

06:39.600 --> 06:41.556
Increase:
WHAT ABOUT THAT YOUNG MAN --

06:41.600 --> 06:43.693
THE ONE WHO WAS TO TAKE HIM
TO BOSTON, HUH?

06:43.730 --> 06:46.164
-Mary: ISAAC?
-Increase: AH.

06:47.170 --> 06:48.728
Mary: ISAAC WILL DO.

06:52.610 --> 06:55.135
HE SLEEPS STILL?

06:55.180 --> 06:57.876
Increase:
UNDER THE CARE OF SENTRIES.

06:57.910 --> 07:00.071
OH, AND, MARY.

07:00.120 --> 07:01.974
BE OF GOOD HEART.

07:02.020 --> 07:05.148
MR. LAMB, THE BARKEEP, TELLS ME
THAT HE MAY WAKE AT ANY MOMENT.

07:12.130 --> 07:13.791
John: COTTON.

07:13.830 --> 07:15.149
COTTON .

07:16.670 --> 07:19.264
Cotton: [ SIGHS ]

07:19.300 --> 07:23.999
NO DIFFERENCE BETWEEN ME
AND THOSE THAT ALREADY REST.

07:24.040 --> 07:25.803
BESIDES A STILL-BEATING HEART

07:25.840 --> 07:28.536
IN A SHELL WHERE MY SOUL
NO LONGER RESIDES.

07:29.680 --> 07:31.602
John: OH, BOY.
[ SIGHS ]

07:38.650 --> 07:40.789
Anne: GOOD MORNING, REVEREND.

07:42.530 --> 07:44.122
I WONDER --

07:44.160 --> 07:46.754
WHAT WOULD IT TAKE
TO GET YOU TO YOUR FEET?

07:46.800 --> 07:49.052
Cotton: WHY WOULD YOU WISH TO?

07:56.340 --> 07:58.331
Anne: I FEARI MAY HAVE...

07:58.370 --> 08:01.806
JUDGED YOU TOO HARSHLY,
REVEREND MATHER.

08:01.840 --> 08:05.469
IT IS ONLY NOW, WHEN LEAVING
MY CHILDHOOD BEHIND,

08:05.510 --> 08:08.547
THAT I REALIZE WE ARE,
PAST AND FOREVER,

08:08.580 --> 08:09.979
OUR FATHERS' CHILDREN.

08:10.020 --> 08:12.784
AND WE CAN NO MORE
CONTROL WHO THEY BE

08:12.820 --> 08:14.685
AND HOW THEY CAME TO FORM US

08:14.720 --> 08:17.689
THEN WE CAN THE RISE AND SETTING
OF THE SUN.

08:19.190 --> 08:21.988
I AM SORRY ABOUT YOUR GIRL.

08:23.070 --> 08:24.992
Cotton: THANK YOU.

08:25.030 --> 08:27.396
Anne: MAY WE SEE YOU HOME?

08:36.610 --> 08:38.271
John: COME ON.

08:47.760 --> 08:50.320
Anne:
ONCE HE'S SE'I'I'LED, CAPTAIN,

08:50.360 --> 08:52.248
MAY I ASK A FAVOR OF YOU?

08:52.290 --> 08:54.850
John: SURELY.

08:54.900 --> 08:56.322
Mary:
"I THINK NOT, MRS. SIBLEY."

08:56.360 --> 08:57.998
[ SCOFFS ]

08:58.030 --> 08:59.839
AS IF HE WERE SOCRATES AND I,
A STUDENT AT HIS KNEE.

08:59.870 --> 09:01.235
Mercy:
LET ME KILL HIM, PLEASE.

09:01.270 --> 09:02.601
Mary: NO.

09:02.640 --> 09:04.335
Mercy:
LET ME EASE THIS BURDEN FOR YOU,

09:04.370 --> 09:06.201
AS I'VE DONE THE OTHERS.
-Mary: INCREASE MATHER IS KNOWN

09:06.240 --> 09:07.878
THROUGHOUT THE WORLD,
NEW AND OLD.

09:07.910 --> 09:10.174
HIS DISAPPEARANCE OR DEATH
WILL NOT BE TAKEN LIGHTLY.

09:10.210 --> 09:11.905
HIS HEAD WILL SIT
ON NO MAN'S PLATTER.

09:11.950 --> 09:13.770
Mercy: HE'S NO MATCH FOR YOU,
CERTAINLY.

09:13.820 --> 09:15.879
Mary: THAT IS WHERE
YOU ARE WRONG, CHILD.

09:15.920 --> 09:18.741
THIS IS OUR TRUEST TEST --
TO BATTLE EQUALS.

09:20.390 --> 09:21.948
Rev. Lewis: MRS. SIBLEY.

09:21.990 --> 09:23.218
Mary: REVEREND.

09:23.260 --> 09:24.682
Rev. Lewis: MERCY.

09:24.730 --> 09:26.254
Mercy: HELLO.

09:26.290 --> 09:28.258
Rev. Lewis: IWONDER
IF I MIGHT HAVE A PRIVATE WORD

09:28.300 --> 09:29.551
WITH MY DAUGHTER.

09:29.600 --> 09:31.727
Mary: I THINK NOT, REVEREND.

09:31.770 --> 09:33.635
-Mercy: I --
-Mary: FETCH ME ISAAC.

09:35.000 --> 09:36.160
NOW.

09:38.440 --> 09:40.738
Rev. Lewis: IAM, UM...

09:40.780 --> 09:45.240
ASTOUNDED AT THE CHARITY
YOU'VE SHOWN MY CHILD,

09:45.280 --> 09:50.081
BUT IF I WISH TO SEE HER,
IS THAT NOT A FATHER'S RIGHT?

09:50.120 --> 09:53.157
Mary: WHY, IN PARTICULAR, DO YOU
WISH TO SEE HER, REVEREND?

09:53.190 --> 09:56.626
WERE YOU PERHAPS CONSIDERING
ANOTHER EXORCISM?

09:56.660 --> 09:58.628
DO YOUR DAYS GROW DULL,

09:58.660 --> 10:00.491
LACKING A CHILD
TO BEAT AND TORTURE

10:00.530 --> 10:03.465
AND THE NIGHTS FAR TOO LONELY
WITH NO DAUGHTER TO VISIT?

10:03.500 --> 10:05.991
-Rev. Lewis: I WOULD NEVER --
-Mary: MERCY IS MINE.

10:06.030 --> 10:09.659
RETURN HERE AGAIN AND THESE
ACCUSATIONS WILL BE MADE PUBLIC.

10:22.690 --> 10:25.284
Tituba: WHAT OF MASTER SIBLEY?
HAS HE WOKEN?

10:26.660 --> 10:28.514
THE ELDERS WILL WAIT NO LONGER.

10:28.560 --> 10:30.881
THEY REQUIRE
AN AUDIENCE WITH YOU TODAY.

10:40.340 --> 10:42.558
Mary: [ SCREAMING ]

10:51.680 --> 10:53.409
Tituba: HAS HE WOKEN?

10:58.550 --> 11:00.359
Mary: ANY MOMENT NOW.

11:06.430 --> 11:08.694
Man: THERE. THERE YOU GO.
THERE YOU GO.

11:12.500 --> 11:14.138
Isaac:
IT WERE AN ACCIDENT, MA'AM.

11:14.170 --> 11:15.535
A WAYWARD TIMBER IN THE PATH,

11:15.570 --> 11:17.709
AND WE FOUND OURSELVES
AT SIXES AND SEVENS.

11:17.740 --> 11:18.832
Mary: IT'S OKAY, ISAAC.

11:18.870 --> 11:20.701
I KNOW YOU'VE DONE YOUR BEST.

11:20.740 --> 11:22.469
Isaac:
THE REVEREND SUMMONS ME NOW,

11:22.510 --> 11:24.808
HEAVEN KNOWS WHY, BUT I FEAR
EACH SECOND HE'S MADE TO WAIT --

11:24.850 --> 11:27.114
Mary: HE WILL ASK YOU
TO WATCH OVER MR. SIBLEY.

11:28.720 --> 11:31.314
-Isaac: HE WILL?
-Mary: AT MY GRAVE INSISTENCE,

11:31.350 --> 11:33.386
SINCE HE REFUSES MY DESIRE

11:33.420 --> 11:35.354
TO BRING MY HUSBAND HOME
TO PROPER CARE.

11:35.390 --> 11:37.255
Isaac: HE REFUSES YOU?

11:37.290 --> 11:40.589
Mary: SALEM REELS OUT OF CONTROL
LIKE AN UNWIELDY SPIN TOP

11:40.630 --> 11:42.427
AT THE WHIM OF INCREASE MATHER.

11:42.460 --> 11:46.863
A TONIC --
THE PAIN AND EASE OF SLEEP.

11:46.900 --> 11:48.333
ISAAC, I BESEECH YOU,

11:48.370 --> 11:50.406
IN THIS MOST PRIVATE
AND IMPORTANT MATTER,

11:50.440 --> 11:51.862
DO MY BIDDING WHERE I CANNOT.

11:51.910 --> 11:53.707
Isaac: OH, UH...

11:53.740 --> 11:56.573
Mary: DOSE HIM IMMEDIATELY
AND KEEP HIM SO.

11:56.610 --> 11:58.601
GEORGE SHOULD NOT
BE MADE TO SUFFER

11:58.650 --> 12:00.948
FOR MATHER SENIOR'S
UNFOUNDED SUSPICIONS.

12:02.890 --> 12:04.619
Isaac: H-HE SHALL NOT.

12:08.790 --> 12:10.724
Mary: AND, ISAAC...

12:12.930 --> 12:14.955
BETWEEN US.

12:15.000 --> 12:17.560
LIKE SO MANY OF SALEM'S SECRETS.

12:18.800 --> 12:20.791
Isaac: BETWEEN US.

12:24.570 --> 12:27.232
-George: [SNORES]
-Increase: ARE YOU AWARE, SON?

12:27.280 --> 12:30.943
YOUR STORY IS KNOWN FAR AND WIDE
THROUGHOUT THE LAND.

12:30.980 --> 12:34.143
ISAAC THE FORNICATOR.

12:34.180 --> 12:38.048
NO, NO, NO.
DO NOT BOW YOUR HEAD IN SHAME.

12:38.090 --> 12:39.887
HEAD UP.
GET YOUR HEAD UP.

12:39.920 --> 12:41.956
HEAD UP. HEAD UP.

12:41.990 --> 12:47.428
THE STORY
OF ISAAC THE FORNICATOR

12:47.460 --> 12:49.428
IS A HOLY ONE.

12:49.460 --> 12:53.237
IT IS USED AS A LIVING PRECEDENT
BY WE PURITANS

12:53.270 --> 12:57.969
TO ILLUSTRATE TO THE CHILDREN
THE EVILS OF LUST.

12:58.010 --> 13:00.808
NO, NO. YOUR SIN
AND YOUR SUFFERING --

13:00.840 --> 13:06.107
IT HAS BEEN TRANSFORMED INTO
A GREAT AND A HOLY BLESSING.

13:06.150 --> 13:09.642
FOR, MY SON...

13:09.680 --> 13:12.148
YOU FELT THE HAND OF GOD.

13:16.360 --> 13:18.328
HE'S TOUCHED YOU.

13:18.360 --> 13:21.158
HE'S WORKING THROUGH YOU.

13:21.200 --> 13:23.122
HE'S CHOSEN YOU.

13:23.170 --> 13:24.626
NO.

13:24.670 --> 13:28.561
HOW MANY CAN SAY THAT THEY
HAVE BEEN CHOSEN BY GOD?

13:29.740 --> 13:31.958
Isaac: CHOSEN FOR WHAT?

13:32.010 --> 13:38.199
Increase: SON, HAVE YOU EVER
IMAGINED A WORLD BEYOND SALEM?

13:38.250 --> 13:40.013
-HMM?
-Isaac: I...

13:40.050 --> 13:41.278
Increase:
GET YOUR HEAD UP, YOUR HEAD UP,

13:41.320 --> 13:44.346
YOUR HEAD UP,
YOUR HEAD UP.

13:44.390 --> 13:46.688
Isaac:
I HAVE A GOOD LIFE HERE, SIR.

13:46.720 --> 13:50.520
Increase: YES, PERFORMING
MEAGER ERRANDS FOR MRS. SIBLEY.

13:50.560 --> 13:53.529
Isaac: SHE'S BEEN GOOD TO ME.
ALWAYS.

13:53.560 --> 13:55.721
Increase: HER CHARITY
BINDS YOU TO HER BIDDING.

13:55.760 --> 13:59.025
[ CLICKS TONGUE ]
NO. NO, NO, NO, ISAAC.

14:00.540 --> 14:03.236
OUT THERE.

14:03.270 --> 14:04.760
OUT THERE, BOY!

14:07.010 --> 14:09.376
THERE'S A VAST WORLD OUT THERE,

14:09.410 --> 14:12.299
FULL OF --
FULL OF OPPORTUNITIES,

14:12.350 --> 14:16.468
AND IF YOU -- IF YOU WOULD
WALK THE STRAIGHT ROAD

14:16.520 --> 14:19.512
IN THE SUNLIGHT
WITH YOUR HEAD UP,

14:19.550 --> 14:22.087
I WOULD TAKE YOU WITH ME
TO SEE IT.

14:22.120 --> 14:23.553
I WOULD.

14:23.590 --> 14:25.023
WOULD YOU LIKE THAT?

14:25.060 --> 14:27.028
Isaac: WHAT WOULD I HAVE TO DO?

14:27.060 --> 14:29.893
Increase: WELL...

14:29.930 --> 14:32.364
YOU WILL HAVE TO --

14:32.400 --> 14:33.992
HAVE TO TEND
TO MR. SIBLEY THERE.

14:34.040 --> 14:35.689
-YOU'LL HAVE TO...
-George: [SNORES]

14:35.740 --> 14:39.164
Increase: ...MAKE CERTAIN
THAT HE IS FRESH AND TIDY,

14:39.210 --> 14:42.941
AND THAT IS NO EASY TASK, HMM?
[ CHUCKLES ]

14:42.980 --> 14:48.373
MOST IMPORTANTLY, YOU MUST ALERT
ME THE MOMENT THAT HE WAKES.

14:49.650 --> 14:51.311
YES.

14:56.590 --> 14:58.126
CAN YOU DO THAT, HMM?

15:00.630 --> 15:03.428
Isaac:
DO YOU MIND ME ASKING, SIR,

15:03.470 --> 15:05.426
WHAT THESE ARE FOR?

15:05.470 --> 15:11.238
Increase: PROTECTION
FOR MR. SIBLEY AGAINST...

15:11.270 --> 15:14.569
OUTER FORCES.

15:14.610 --> 15:17.306
-IT'S CREMATED ASH...
-Isaac: [CHUCKLES]

15:17.350 --> 15:20.945
Increase:
...OF A 200-YEAR-OLD WITCH.

15:20.980 --> 15:22.174
AND, ISAAC...

15:25.350 --> 15:27.318
I BURNED HER MYSELF.

15:30.490 --> 15:34.096
Anne: SO, THE ROOF NEEDS
PATCHING THERE AND THERE,

15:34.130 --> 15:35.791
A FRESH COAT OF PAINT
WOULDN'T HURT,

15:35.830 --> 15:38.094
NOR WOULD FOUR OR FIVE MORE BEDS
FOR THE SMALLER CHILDREN,

15:38.130 --> 15:41.634
AND -- I'M OVERWHELMING YOU.

15:41.670 --> 15:42.830
John: NO, NO.

15:42.870 --> 15:44.735
I'M EAGER TO PUT MY ENERGIES
TO GOOD.

15:44.770 --> 15:46.362
Anne: EXACTLY.

15:52.480 --> 15:55.313
THE CHILDREN ARE FRIGHTENED,
CAPTAIN.

15:55.350 --> 15:59.741
ANOTHER HUNG TODAY AND
NOT AN INKLING WHO'S TO BE NEXT.

15:59.790 --> 16:02.452
THEY'RE UNSURE
WHO TO FEAR MORE --

16:02.490 --> 16:05.084
WITCHES
OR THOSE WHO PURSUE THEM.

16:05.130 --> 16:07.519
John: WELL, WHO CAN BLAME THEM?

16:09.230 --> 16:12.119
HE DOESN'T PLAY WITH THE OTHERS.

16:12.170 --> 16:13.831
THE DARK-HAIRED BOY.

16:15.370 --> 16:17.634
Anne: HE'S BEEN HERE TWO YEARS.

16:17.670 --> 16:19.809
HIS PARENTS
WERE MURDERED BY INDIANS.

16:19.840 --> 16:23.048
THEY SAY HE SAW.

16:23.080 --> 16:25.469
NO ONE KNOWS HOW HE SURVIVED.

16:25.510 --> 16:28.775
John: HAS ANYONE ASKED?

16:28.820 --> 16:30.981
Anne: HE DOESN'T TALK.

16:31.020 --> 16:34.217
AT LEAST, NOT ANYMORE.

16:34.260 --> 16:38.048
NOT SINCE...THEN.

16:44.600 --> 16:46.090
John: EXCUSE ME.

16:48.500 --> 16:51.037
DO YOU KNOW ANYTHING
ABOUT PATCHING A ROOF?

16:58.210 --> 17:00.519
Mercy: MRS. SIBLEY?

17:00.550 --> 17:02.814
Tituba: THE MISTRESS IS OUT.

17:02.850 --> 17:04.647
Mercy: OH.

17:04.690 --> 17:07.250
Tituba: ANYTHING NEEDED TO BE
SAID TO HER CAN BE SAID TO ME.

17:13.360 --> 17:16.193
Mercy: OH, THAT'S BEAUTIFUL!

17:18.070 --> 17:20.129
Titu ba: MY FAMILIAR.

17:23.440 --> 17:24.862
Mercy: FAMILIAR?

17:24.910 --> 17:28.903
Tituba: A GIFT
FROM THE DEVIL TO DO MY BIDDING,

17:28.940 --> 17:31.044
MY SPIRITUAL COMPANION.

17:35.220 --> 17:37.142
THIS IS HOW SHE FEEDS.

17:43.490 --> 17:44.479
Mercy: [ CHUCKLES ]

17:48.100 --> 17:50.125
WILL I GET A FAMILIAR?

17:50.170 --> 17:52.195
Tituba: IN TIME.

17:52.230 --> 17:54.892
Mercy: HOW DO I CHOOSE?

17:54.940 --> 17:56.191
Tituba: YOU DON'T.

17:56.240 --> 17:57.730
IT CHOOSES YOU.

18:18.530 --> 18:20.418
[ BELL CHIMING ]

18:28.470 --> 18:31.564
Together:
GOOD DAY, MRS. SIBLEY.

18:31.610 --> 18:34.101
Mary: GIRLS.

18:34.140 --> 18:36.973
Dollie: WE'RE OFF
TO MEET MERCY IN THE GRAVEYARD.

18:38.180 --> 18:39.738
Mary: WELL.

18:39.780 --> 18:41.441
ON YOUR WAY, THEN.

19:05.140 --> 19:06.664
[ BUBBLING ]

19:10.580 --> 19:13.344
WE ALL GRIEVE
THE LOSS OF OUR SISTER.

19:27.200 --> 19:29.828
I DO NOT ARGUE THIS.

19:29.860 --> 19:32.829
BUT BEG REMEMBRANCE
THAT I WAS GIVEN LITTLE CHOICE.

19:35.700 --> 19:37.167
THE MALUM...

19:37.210 --> 19:38.837
[ BOTH GASP ]

19:38.870 --> 19:42.033
...WITHOUT WHICH OUR GRAND RITE
WOULD NOT BE POSSIBLE.

19:53.220 --> 19:57.224
ROSE BROUGHT IT HERE,
THIS INSTRUMENT OF DEATH,

19:57.260 --> 20:01.219
WITHOUT MY KNOWLEDGE,
TO CHALLENGE AND DEFEAT ME.

20:01.260 --> 20:03.262
[ CAULDRON SIZZLES, BUBBLES ]

20:14.740 --> 20:19.074
IT IS FOR YOU,
RETRIEVED AT GREAT COST,

20:19.110 --> 20:22.568
RELINQUISHED WITH
LOVE AND ARDOR FOR OUR CAUSE.

20:24.050 --> 20:25.711
I LEAVE YOU NOW
WITH THE ONLY TOOL

20:25.750 --> 20:27.786
THAT EXISTS ON EARTH
TO CONTROL ME.

20:48.340 --> 20:49.739
[ CHILDREN LAUGHING ]

20:51.580 --> 20:55.710
John: THE TRICK TO MAKING SHAKES
IS TO SPLIT THEM --

20:55.750 --> 20:59.117
NOT CHOPPED OR SAWN,
BUT TO SPLIT.

20:59.150 --> 21:00.856
THANK YOU.

21:04.930 --> 21:06.750
[ TAPPING ]

21:08.630 --> 21:10.097
YOUR TURN.

21:16.000 --> 21:18.434
RIGHT! WELL DONE.
[ CHUCKLES ]

21:18.470 --> 21:20.108
Mary: CAPTAIN.

21:21.510 --> 21:23.546
John: MRS. SIBLEY.

21:24.710 --> 21:25.938
Mary: YOUNG MAN.

21:27.520 --> 21:30.148
John: WHY DON'T YOU GO SEE IF
THERE'S ANY FRESH WATER, HUH?

21:36.560 --> 21:38.289
BIG DOINGS THIS MORNING.

21:38.330 --> 21:41.026
Mary: SEEMS EVERY DAY BRINGS
ITS FAIR SHARE OF SURPRISES.

21:41.060 --> 21:43.528
John: I HEARD OLD INCREASE
TOOK POSSESSION OF YOUR HUSBAND.

21:43.570 --> 21:44.798
Mary: YES, HE DID.

21:44.830 --> 21:46.525
AND I'M EAGER TO GET HIM BACK.

21:46.570 --> 21:48.231
John: YOU ARE?

21:50.670 --> 21:51.705
WHY?

21:53.880 --> 21:55.802
Mary:
IS IT SO UNUSUAL, CAPTAIN,

21:55.840 --> 21:57.876
FOR A WIFE TO WANT HER HUSBAND
AT HOME?

21:57.910 --> 22:01.676
John: IN MOST CASES,
IT'S NOT UNUSUAL AT ALL.

22:01.720 --> 22:04.883
Anne: I HEARD MY HARD WORKER
WAS THIRSTY.

22:04.920 --> 22:07.013
OH, MRS. SIBLEY.

22:07.050 --> 22:08.483
UH, FRESH APPLE WATER ON OFFER.

22:08.520 --> 22:10.784
Mary:
NO, THANK YOU, ANNE.

22:10.830 --> 22:12.923
GOOD DAY, CAPTAIN. YOUNG MAN.

22:17.100 --> 22:18.761
Anne: CAPTAIN.

22:38.250 --> 22:39.615
[ DOOR OPENS ]

22:48.760 --> 22:50.057
Cotton: MAY I?

23:25.170 --> 23:27.661
-Cotton: SIR.
-Man: GOOD MORROW.

23:30.340 --> 23:33.776
Increase: IF YOU'RE GOING TO
CAPITULATE TO YOUR WEAKN ESS,

23:33.810 --> 23:37.132
MUST IT BE ON CONSTANT
PUBLIC DISPLAY?

23:37.180 --> 23:40.809
Cotton: SHALL I LEAVE
PUBLIC DISPLAY TO YOU, FATHER?

23:41.980 --> 23:43.538
SHALL WE ABOLISH THE NOOSE

23:43.590 --> 23:46.548
SO THAT YOU MAY BREAK NECKS
WITH YOUR OWN TWO HANDS?

23:46.590 --> 23:48.148
Increase: SHE WAS DEAD.

23:50.320 --> 23:53.494
THE WHORE RUNNER KILLED HERSELF.

23:53.530 --> 23:56.328
Cotton: SHE WAS ALREADY DEAD,

23:56.360 --> 23:57.622
AND YET YOU HUNG HER.

23:57.670 --> 23:59.558
Increase: I SAID SHE WOULD HANG.

23:59.600 --> 24:01.739
AND HANG SHE DID.

24:01.770 --> 24:04.659
WE ARE NOTHING
IF WE DO NOT KEEP OUR WORD,

24:04.710 --> 24:09.033
A PRINCIPLE WHICH SEEMS TO MEAN
VERY LITTLE TO YOU, I FEAR.

24:10.710 --> 24:13.099
Cotton: MUST YOU HATE ME SO?

24:13.150 --> 24:15.038
Increase: OH, COTTON.

24:17.280 --> 24:21.319
YOUR MOTHER WAS A COTTON,
AS YOU KNOW.

24:21.360 --> 24:23.988
AND MY STEPSISTER.

24:24.030 --> 24:27.625
OUR MARRIAGE WAS
A HISTORICAL INEVITABILITY.

24:27.660 --> 24:29.628
THE COTTONS AND THE MATHERS --

24:29.660 --> 24:31.525
WHO COULD RESIST SUCH A --

24:31.570 --> 24:35.529
SUCH A JOINING OF --
OF POWER AND PRESTIGE?

24:35.570 --> 24:38.334
Cotton: CERTAINLY NOT YOU.

24:38.370 --> 24:41.203
Increase:
SHE WAS A GOOD WOMAN,

24:41.240 --> 24:43.879
AND SHE WAS A FIT ENOUGH MOTHER,

24:43.910 --> 24:47.346
BUT...

24:47.380 --> 24:49.018
I DIDN'T LOVE HER.

24:51.520 --> 24:54.080
I DIDN'T LOVE.

24:55.660 --> 24:57.651
AND THEN YOU WERE BORN.

24:57.690 --> 24:58.884
[ CHUCKLES ]

24:58.930 --> 25:02.297
AND THERE YOU WERE, A...

25:02.330 --> 25:07.563
SQUALLING MESS OF LIMBS
AND OF HAIR, AND...

25:07.600 --> 25:10.728
YOU WEREN'T MUCH.

25:10.770 --> 25:13.534
BUT YOU WERE ENOUGH
TO SHOW ME LOVE.

25:14.780 --> 25:17.499
Cotton: [ SNIFFS ]

25:17.550 --> 25:20.576
WHAT UTTER IRONY

25:20.620 --> 25:25.080
THAT YOU WOULD THEN TAKE
THE SELF-SAME THING FROM ME.

25:25.120 --> 25:26.985
[ CLA'I'I'ERING ]
Henry: AH!

25:27.020 --> 25:29.159
Lamb: YOU ARE CUT OFF, SIR!

25:29.190 --> 25:31.750
Henry: [ Slurring ]
NO. I HAVE MONEY!

25:31.790 --> 25:34.657
I WILL DRINK MUCHLY AND OFTEN!

25:34.700 --> 25:36.429
Lamb: YOU WILL NOT.
NOW BE ON YOUR WAY.

25:36.460 --> 25:39.224
-Henry: I THINK NOT.
-Lamb: OH, NO, NO. WHOA. GO!

25:39.270 --> 25:41.431
Henry: [ SHOUTING INDISTINCTLY ]

25:46.570 --> 25:48.538
Increase: THE WINE IS FROM GOD.

25:49.710 --> 25:52.247
THE DRUNKARD IS FROM THE DEVIL.

26:05.290 --> 26:07.178
PULL YOURSELF TOGETHER.

26:07.230 --> 26:09.050
THERE'S MUCH WORK TO BE DONE.

26:19.470 --> 26:20.630
Mercy: LET ME KILL HIM.

26:20.680 --> 26:21.977
Mary: I HAVE TOLD YOU.

26:22.010 --> 26:24.069
WE CANNOT KILL INCREASE.

26:24.110 --> 26:26.146
Mercy: NOT SILLY OLD INCREASE.

26:26.180 --> 26:27.545
MR. SIBLEY.

26:27.580 --> 26:29.218
Tituba:
THIS IS WHAT YOU TEACH HER?

26:29.250 --> 26:32.913
FOR ANY PROBLEM, MURDER
IS THE FIRST COURSE OF ACTION?

26:34.020 --> 26:36.079
Mary: WE CANNOT KILL GEORGE.

26:36.120 --> 26:37.951
Mercy: WHY NOT?

26:37.990 --> 26:41.494
YOU ARE SO POWERFUL --
YOU ALONE.

26:41.530 --> 26:44.169
-YOU DO NOT NEED HIM.
-Mary: [ CHUCKLES]

26:44.200 --> 26:46.259
THAT IS WHERE YOU ARE WRONG,
MY DEAR.

26:46.300 --> 26:48.837
WE NEED HIM DESPERATELY.

26:48.870 --> 26:51.509
WITHOUT GEORGE,
IT ALL GOES AWAY.

26:51.540 --> 26:53.565
I AM A WIDOW WITH NOTHING --

26:53.610 --> 26:57.330
NO BUSINESS TO RUN,
NO VOICE WITH THE SELECTMEN.

26:57.380 --> 26:59.940
WITH HIM ALIVE,
I CAN SPEAK THROUGH HIM --

26:59.980 --> 27:03.074
A PUPPET TO PARROT
HIS WISHES AND THOUGHTS.

27:03.120 --> 27:07.910
BUT DEAD, HE IS USELESS
AND I AM WITHOUT POWER.

27:07.960 --> 27:10.520
Mercy: BUT HOW WILL YOU STOP HIM
FROM SPEAKING?

27:10.560 --> 27:13.449
Mary: I WILL ENTER HIS MIND
AND DESTROY IT FROM WITHIN.

27:13.490 --> 27:16.197
HIS BODY WILL LIVE ON,
BUT HIS MIND WILL BE GONE.

27:16.230 --> 27:17.663
Mercy:
HOW WILL YOU DO THAT?

27:17.700 --> 27:19.861
Tituba: QUIET GIRL!
THAT IS ENOUGH QUESTIONS.

27:19.900 --> 27:21.197
Mercy:
DON'T YOU TELL ME TO BE QUIET.

27:21.240 --> 27:23.128
-Tituba: QUIET.
-Mary: ENOUGH!

27:23.170 --> 27:25.661
BOTH OF YOU, LEAVE ME NOW.

27:25.710 --> 27:27.337
-Tituba: BUT I CAN HELP YOU.
-Mary: GET OUT!

27:33.080 --> 27:34.308
Mercy: LET GO OF ME!

27:34.350 --> 27:36.147
-Tituba: SHH!
-Mercy: LET GO!

27:36.180 --> 27:37.841
Tituba:
YOU KNOW WHO WE COULD KILL?

27:37.890 --> 27:39.141
YOU.

27:39.190 --> 27:41.215
Mercy: YOU CAN'T.
SHE WOULD NEVER LET YOU.

27:41.260 --> 27:43.615
Tituba: MAYBE, MAYBE NOT.

27:43.660 --> 27:46.185
YOU DON'T WANT TO FIND OUT.

27:46.230 --> 27:49.825
Mercy: YOU'RE JEALOUS
AND SPITEFUL AND AWFUL.

27:49.860 --> 27:53.796
Tituba: YEARS --
I HAVE WAITED MANY, MANY YEARS.

27:53.840 --> 27:56.729
STAY OUT OF MY WAY,
YOU LITTLE BITCH.

27:56.770 --> 27:59.102
Mercy: [ BREATHING HEAVILY]

28:05.180 --> 28:09.617
Isaac: MRS. SIBLEY'S ONLY EVER
HAD YOUR BEST INTEREST AT HEART.

28:10.950 --> 28:13.817
YET STILL...

28:13.860 --> 28:16.078
YOUR MOMENT'S WORST DESPERATION,

28:16.120 --> 28:18.486
IT WAS NOT HER NAME
YOU UTTERED FOR RESCUE

28:18.530 --> 28:21.226
BUT THAT OF
THE REVEREND MATHER SENIOR.

28:21.260 --> 28:24.866
WHAT DO I,

28:24.900 --> 28:29.394
WHO HAVE KNOWN ONLY VIOLENCE AND
MALICE FROM YOUR EAGER HANDS,

28:29.440 --> 28:33.228
CARE A WHIT
ABOUT YOUR ROSY OUTLOOK?

28:47.450 --> 28:49.987
George: [ GAGGING ]

28:51.890 --> 28:53.824
[GULPS]

29:01.400 --> 29:03.095
MARY.

29:04.470 --> 29:06.062
MARY.

29:10.610 --> 29:14.068
FREE OF YOUR PRECIOUS FAMILIAR,

29:14.120 --> 29:15.974
I FINALLY GOT HOLD
OF MY DREAMS BACK.

29:16.020 --> 29:17.988
Mary: HMM. A BEATIFIC CHOICE

29:18.020 --> 29:20.113
FOR SUCH
A DARK AND TWISTED MIND.

29:20.150 --> 29:22.618
George: [ CHUCKLES ]

29:22.660 --> 29:24.252
YOU REMEMBER COMING HERE?

29:24.290 --> 29:27.327
-Mary: YES. A PICNIC.
-George: [ CHUCKLES ]

29:27.360 --> 29:30.796
Mary: THE ONE AND ONLY DAY
I ALMOST DIDN'T DESPISE YOU.

29:30.830 --> 29:32.491
George:
YOU NEVER GAVE ME A CHANCE.

29:32.530 --> 29:34.737
YOUR MIND WAS LONG MADE UP.

29:34.770 --> 29:36.499
Mary: [ CHUCKLES]
CAN YOU BLAME ME?

29:36.540 --> 29:38.565
YOU STOLE MY LIFE.

29:38.610 --> 29:40.066
George:
AND NOW YOU'VE STOLEN MINE.

29:40.110 --> 29:41.771
Mary: WE ARE CLOSE.

29:41.810 --> 29:44.142
SO VERY CLOSE.

29:44.180 --> 29:47.069
THE GRAND RITE
IS ALMOST COMPLETE.

29:47.110 --> 29:48.316
George: AND THEN WHAT?

29:48.350 --> 29:50.238
ANOTHER KINGDOM FOR YOU TO RULE?

29:50.280 --> 29:51.816
Mary: YES.

29:51.850 --> 29:54.410
A WORLD IN WHICH
I NO LONGER NEED YOU.

29:54.460 --> 29:57.418
A BLESSED WORLD IN WHICH
YOU CAN FINALLY DIE.

29:57.460 --> 29:58.688
George: PERIL AND THREATS.

29:58.730 --> 30:00.925
Mary:
MANY A UNION HAS RELIED ON LESS.

30:00.960 --> 30:03.656
[ CHUCKLES ]
DON'T LOOK SO WORRIED, GEORGE.

30:03.700 --> 30:06.191
WE'RE A LITTLE WAYS OFF YET.

30:06.230 --> 30:08.767
FOR NOW, I JUST NEED YOU QUIET,

30:08.800 --> 30:14.477
SLEEPING LIKE AN ANGEL
IN YOUR DIRTY BIBS AND NAPPIES.

30:35.330 --> 30:37.389
FAREWELL, GEORGE.

30:42.670 --> 30:44.900
George: YOU BITCH!
YOU BITCH!

30:57.450 --> 30:59.338
Mary: [ GASPS ]

30:59.390 --> 31:00.846
OH, THAT BASTARD.

31:00.890 --> 31:03.188
-Tituba: SIBLEY?
-Mary: INCREASE MATHER.

31:03.220 --> 31:06.553
HE WAS THERE.

31:06.590 --> 31:08.649
PROTECTING GEORGE.

31:08.700 --> 31:13.262
GUARDING HIS MIND EVEN IN SLEEP.

31:13.300 --> 31:15.894
Tituba:
WE HAVE ANOTHER PROBLEM.

31:15.940 --> 31:18.431
WE MUST DO SOMETHING
ABOUT THE GIRL.

31:18.470 --> 31:19.732
Mary: [ SIGHS ] MERCY.

31:19.770 --> 31:22.102
Tituba: SHE IS...UNRELIABLE.

31:22.140 --> 31:24.040
IT IS ONLY
A MATTER OF TIME BEFORE

31:24.080 --> 31:25.502
WE CAN NO LONGER CONTROL HER.

31:25.550 --> 31:28.041
Mary: AT A TIME SUCH AS THIS

31:28.080 --> 31:30.776
WHEN I AM NEARER
TO DISCOVERY AND ANNIHILATION

31:30.820 --> 31:32.048
THAN EVER BEFORE,

31:32.090 --> 31:33.682
YOU WOULD DISTRACT YOURSELF

31:33.720 --> 31:36.518
WITH PETTY JEALOUSY
AND SPITEFUL ACCUSATIONS.

31:36.560 --> 31:37.879
Tituba:
I AM TRYING TO MAKE --

31:37.930 --> 31:39.955
Mary:
NEVER HAVE I NEEDED YOU MORE.

31:39.990 --> 31:42.356
AND NEVER HAVE YOU
DISAPPOINTED ME SO GRAVELY.

31:42.400 --> 31:44.721
Tituba:
I WOULD DO ANYTHING FOR YOU.

31:44.770 --> 31:46.067
I LOVE YOU.

31:46.100 --> 31:48.568
Mary: OH,
AND I WISH TO GOD YOU DIDN'T.

31:48.600 --> 31:52.309
LOVE ME LESS
AND YOU WILL LOVE ME BETTER.

31:52.340 --> 31:54.331
FIND A WAY TO GET TO GEORGE.

31:58.250 --> 32:01.071
John: TOMORROW,
WE'LL WORK ON THE PAINT.

32:01.120 --> 32:03.611
THAT IS, IF YOU'RE STILL
AVAILABLE, OF COURSE.

32:03.650 --> 32:05.242
EXCELLENT.

32:05.290 --> 32:07.485
EXCELLENT, SON.

32:11.630 --> 32:14.098
Stephen: STEPHEN.

32:15.600 --> 32:17.818
John: STEPHEN.

32:17.860 --> 32:19.919
Henry:
YOU'VE SEEN MY DAUGHTER.

32:21.670 --> 32:23.729
John: YOU CAN MOVE ALONG.
THERE'S KIDS HERE.

32:23.770 --> 32:26.159
Henry:
I'M LOOKING FOR A KID -- MY KID.

32:26.210 --> 32:28.132
John:
AND I SAID, "MOVE ALONG."

32:28.180 --> 32:30.000
Anne: MR. HOPKINS.

32:30.040 --> 32:32.304
HOW CAN WE HELP YOU?

32:32.350 --> 32:35.319
Henry: MY DAUGHTER CAME TO STAY
HERE AFTER WHEN I WAS IN JAIL?

32:35.350 --> 32:36.749
Anne: EMILY?

32:36.780 --> 32:38.941
NO, MR. HOPKINS. SHE DID NOT.

32:38.990 --> 32:40.787
Henry:
HAVE YOU SEEN HER AROUND?

32:40.820 --> 32:43.084
Anne: NO, SIR. I HAVEN'T.

32:43.120 --> 32:46.453
Henry: OH.

32:46.490 --> 32:49.948
YOU TELL HER
I'M LOOKING FOR HER.

32:50.000 --> 32:52.525
YOU TELL HER
SHE NEEDS TO COME HOME.

32:54.370 --> 32:56.463
Anne: YES, MR. HOPKINS.
I'LL DO THAT.

33:03.640 --> 33:06.006
Dollie: LIZZY...DID YOU BRING
THE CHICKEN FEATHERS

33:06.050 --> 33:07.642
AND THE DRIED HORSE DUNG?

33:07.680 --> 33:10.615
Elizabeth: I BRUNG THE FEATHERS,
BUT THE DUNG WEREN'T DRY.

33:10.650 --> 33:12.379
Dollie:
AND WHAT ABOUT THE MICE?

33:12.420 --> 33:15.810
Emily: THEY SCATTERED
WHEN THE CAT COME TO THE TRAP.

33:15.860 --> 33:18.124
Dollie:
MERCY IS TO BE HERE ANY MINUTE.

33:18.160 --> 33:21.197
MUST I DO EVERYTHING MYSELF?

33:28.870 --> 33:31.839
Anne: MISS HOPKINS,
MAY I HAVE A WORD?

33:37.040 --> 33:38.598
YOUR FATHER HAS BEEN FREED.

33:40.250 --> 33:41.512
Emily: I SEE.

33:41.550 --> 33:44.383
Anne:
AND HE'S BEEN LOOKING FOR YOU,

33:44.420 --> 33:48.186
ASKS THAT YOU COME HOME
IMMEDIATELY.

33:48.220 --> 33:49.619
Mercy: MISS HALE.

33:55.730 --> 33:58.597
CAN WE HELP YOU?

33:59.930 --> 34:01.329
Anne: I'VE ONLY COME
TO TELL MISS HOPKINS

34:01.370 --> 34:02.860
THAT HER FATHER HAS BEEN FREED.

34:04.870 --> 34:06.804
Mercy: HOW KIND.

34:09.980 --> 34:11.868
Anne: AND THAT HE SEEMED...

34:11.910 --> 34:14.879
QUITE INEBRIATED
AND NOT HIMSELF,

34:14.920 --> 34:16.842
AND THAT PERHAPS
SHE OUGHTN'T TO GO HOME TONIGHT.

34:16.880 --> 34:19.383
PERHAPS SHE OUGHT TO STAY IN THE
ORPHANAGE WHERE SHE'D BE SAFE.

34:19.420 --> 34:21.718
Mercy: SHE IS SAFE.

34:21.760 --> 34:23.409
WITH US.

34:23.460 --> 34:26.554
Anne: IS SHE?

34:30.900 --> 34:34.028
Mercy:
WOULD YOU CARE TO STAY AND...

34:34.070 --> 34:37.528
SEE FOR YOURSELF...

34:37.570 --> 34:38.935
ANNE?

34:45.780 --> 34:48.419
Anne: NOT TONIGHT.

34:57.760 --> 35:00.729
[ DOOR OPENS ]
Increase: STOP.

35:00.760 --> 35:02.648
WHAT IS THAT?

35:04.530 --> 35:07.658
Isaac:
A TONIC. FOR PAIN.

35:11.970 --> 35:13.437
Increase:
WHERE DID YOU GET IT?

35:13.470 --> 35:16.075
Isaac: MR. LAMB GAVE IT TO ME

35:16.110 --> 35:17.930
WHILE YOU WERE OUT.
-Increase: NO.

35:17.980 --> 35:19.845
Isaac: NO?

35:19.880 --> 35:22.576
Increase: [ CLICKS TONGUE ]
YOUNG MAN...

35:22.620 --> 35:25.145
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

35:25.190 --> 35:29.957
YOUNG MAN, I OFFERED YOU
AN OPPORTUNITY, DID I NOT?

35:29.990 --> 35:31.457
DO YOU REMEMBER?

35:31.490 --> 35:35.096
THE WORLD --
THE VAST WORLD, THE SUNLIGHT.

35:35.130 --> 35:36.995
I SOMEHOW SUSPECTED YOU WOULD
FIND A WAY

35:37.030 --> 35:38.691
TO UNDERMINE YOURSELF.

35:38.730 --> 35:40.459
BUT I DID -- I HOPED AGAINST
HOPE THAT YOU WOULDN'T,

35:40.500 --> 35:42.365
BUT YOU DID.

35:42.400 --> 35:46.131
BECAUSE NOT ONLY ARE YOU
A CRETIN, YOU'RE A FAILURE.

35:46.170 --> 35:48.502
YOU'RE A CRETINOUS FAILURE,
AND LIKE ALL FAILURES,

35:48.540 --> 35:51.543
YOU SAY TO YOURSELF,
"BUT I NEVER GET THE CHANCE!

35:51.580 --> 35:56.643
I NEVER GET THE OPPORTUNITY,"
BUT IT JUST AIN'T SO, IS IT?

35:56.680 --> 35:58.045
NO.

35:58.080 --> 36:00.810
AND LIKE EVERY FAILURE,
WHAT DO YOU DO?

36:00.850 --> 36:04.786
YOU JUST PISS
IN THE WELL OF POSSIBILITY.

36:04.830 --> 36:09.494
AND NOW YOU ARE GOING TO TELL ME
WHO GAVE YOU THE POTION.

36:10.660 --> 36:12.969
Dollie: STIFF AS A STICK,
COLD AS A MARBLE.

36:13.000 --> 36:15.366
Elizabeth: LIGHT AS A SPIRIT,
LIFT YOURSELF.

36:15.400 --> 36:17.664
-Woman: LIGHT AS A FEATHER,
STIFF AS A BOARD.

36:17.700 --> 36:20.066
-Woman #2: LIGHT AS A FEATHER,
STIFF AS A BOARD.

36:20.110 --> 36:21.975
-Woman #3: LIGHT AS A FEATHER,
STIFF AS A BOARD.

36:22.010 --> 36:24.649
-Woman: MASTER SPIDER,
STILTED OR STIFLED...

36:24.680 --> 36:26.875
A||:
SPIN US A WEB AND HEED OUR CALL.

36:26.910 --> 36:29.413
MASTER SPIDER,
STILTED OR STIFLED,

36:29.450 --> 36:31.680
SPIN US A WEB AND HEED OUR CALL.

36:31.720 --> 36:33.642
MASTER SPIDER,
STILTED OR STIFLED...

36:33.690 --> 36:34.918
Increase: WHO GAVE IT YOU?

36:34.960 --> 36:38.885
Isaac: [ WHIMPERS ]

36:38.930 --> 36:41.398
Increase:
HMM? WHO GAVE IT YOU?

36:41.430 --> 36:43.489
[SLAP]

36:43.530 --> 36:45.327
HEAD UP. HEAD UP.

36:45.370 --> 36:47.167
-IsaaC: IT'S NOT A POTION.
-Increase: IT'S NOT A POTION?

36:47.200 --> 36:48.667
Isaac: IT'S NOT A PO--

36:48.700 --> 36:50.668
[ CRYING ]

36:50.700 --> 36:51.837
Increase: LOOK AT ME, BOY.

36:51.870 --> 36:53.667
Isaac:
IT'S -- IT'S MEDICINE.

36:53.710 --> 36:55.029
Increase: ONE MORE TIME.

36:55.080 --> 36:56.707
Isaac: [ GRUNTS ]

36:56.740 --> 37:00.107
Increase: I'M GOING TO ASK YOU,
WHO GAVE IT TO YOU?

37:00.150 --> 37:02.618
All: MASTER SPIDER,
STILTED OR STIFLED,

37:02.650 --> 37:04.789
SPIN US A WEB AND HEED OUR CALL.

37:04.820 --> 37:07.448
MASTER SPIDER,
STILTED OR STIFLED...

37:07.490 --> 37:10.618
Increase:
WHAT WE'LL DO IS THIS --

37:10.660 --> 37:12.685
Isaac: IT'S MEDICINE.

37:12.730 --> 37:13.958
Increase: SHH, SHH.

37:13.990 --> 37:15.526
I'M GOING TO SLIT YOUR BELLY
OPEN.

37:15.560 --> 37:17.096
Isaac:
[ Crying ] IT'S MEDICINE.

37:17.130 --> 37:19.121
Increase:
I'M GOING TO REACH IN, PULL OUT,

37:19.170 --> 37:21.638
AND I'M GOING TO THROTTLE YOU
WITH YOUR OWN INTESTINES.

37:21.670 --> 37:22.967
All: ...HEED OUR CALL.

37:23.000 --> 37:25.264
MASTER SPIDER,
STILTED OR STIFLED,

37:25.310 --> 37:27.562
SPIN US A WEB AND HEED OUR CALL.

37:27.610 --> 37:30.204
MASTER SPIDER,
STILTED OR STIFLED...

37:30.240 --> 37:31.901
Isaac: NO. NO. NO.

37:31.950 --> 37:33.872
Increase:
NOW, YOU TELL ME RIGHT NOW,

37:33.910 --> 37:35.446
WHO GAVE IT TO YOU?!

37:36.450 --> 37:38.714
TELL ME, ISAAC!

37:38.750 --> 37:40.889
TELL ME!

37:40.920 --> 37:44.549
Isaac: MRS. SIBLEY COULD BRING
NO HARM TO A LIVING THING.

37:44.590 --> 37:47.081
IF -- IF SHE PROVIDED ME
THE MEDICINE,

37:47.130 --> 37:48.449
THAT'S GOOD ENOUGH FOR ME.

37:54.000 --> 37:56.434
Increase: MRS. SIBLEY, EH?

37:56.470 --> 37:57.732
[ SIGHS ]

37:57.770 --> 38:00.500
WELL DONE.

38:00.540 --> 38:02.269
OFF WITH YOU NOW.

38:02.310 --> 38:04.198
Isaac: [ WHIMPERING ]

38:07.150 --> 38:08.845
Increase: GO.

38:08.880 --> 38:11.269
GO ON! OUT OF MY SIGHT!

38:11.320 --> 38:14.312
ISAAC THE FORNICATOR!

38:16.820 --> 38:20.358
George: [ GAGGING ]

38:20.390 --> 38:21.789
Increase: GEORGE.

38:21.830 --> 38:22.922
George: [ COUGHING ]

38:22.960 --> 38:24.029
Increase: GEORGE!

38:24.060 --> 38:28.429
George: [ GASPING ]

38:28.470 --> 38:29.789
Increase: GEORGE!

38:35.080 --> 38:36.377
Henry: HEY.

38:40.250 --> 38:42.969
Emily: HELLO, FATHER.

38:43.020 --> 38:44.681
Henry:
TOLD YOU I'D GET OUT.

38:44.720 --> 38:46.984
Emily: YES, YOU DID.

38:47.020 --> 38:49.511
Henry:
I TOLD YOU THIS WEREN'T OVER.

38:49.560 --> 38:52.950
YOU'LL BE SOLD STILL,
IF THE WHORES WILL HAVE YOU.

38:52.990 --> 38:55.299
Emily:
I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

38:55.330 --> 38:57.150
Henry: YOU WILL.

38:57.200 --> 39:00.499
YOU WILL GO WHERE I TELL YOU!

39:00.530 --> 39:01.997
Emily: I WON'T.

39:04.570 --> 39:06.868
[ Crying ] IWON'T. I --

39:06.910 --> 39:08.639
[ CRYING ]

39:08.680 --> 39:09.874
PLEASE!

39:09.910 --> 39:11.878
[ BLOWS LANDING,
EMILY SCREAMING ]

39:17.780 --> 39:20.010
Dollie: HENRY HOPKINS.

39:38.440 --> 39:40.101
Henry: WHAT IS THIS?

39:41.040 --> 39:42.075
HEY!

39:43.640 --> 39:46.609
[ ALL SHOUTING ]

39:55.960 --> 39:58.110
AAH!

39:58.160 --> 40:01.379
Emily: [ GIGGLES ]

40:04.470 --> 40:06.290
John: STEPHEN.

40:06.330 --> 40:08.890
THAT'S HIS NAME, THE BOY.

40:08.940 --> 40:10.259
Anne: HE TOLD YOU?

40:10.300 --> 40:11.801
John: YEP.

40:11.840 --> 40:13.603
Anne: [ LAUGHS ]

40:13.640 --> 40:15.198
TWO YEARS WITHOUT SPEAKING,

40:15.240 --> 40:17.538
AND IN ONE DAY,
HE TELLS YOU HIS NAME.

40:17.580 --> 40:20.549
HE MUST HAVE REALLY
TAKEN TO YOU, CAPTAIN.

40:20.580 --> 40:22.218
John:
NO, I WOULDN'T SAY THAT.

40:22.250 --> 40:24.241
Anne:
AND WHO COULD BLAME HIM?

40:24.280 --> 40:28.284
John: BOYS NEED ATTENTION

40:28.320 --> 40:31.483
AND HARD WORK
TO BURN OFF THEIR ENERGY.

40:31.530 --> 40:33.157
Anne: AND I'M GRATEFUL...

40:33.190 --> 40:36.455
FOR YOUR HARD WORK.

40:36.500 --> 40:39.264
John: IT'S THE FIRST HOURS
PASSED SINCE I'VE COME BACK

40:39.300 --> 40:42.963
WHERE I HAVEN'T
THOUGHT ABOUT WITCHES.

40:43.000 --> 40:44.763
Anne: [ CHUCKLES ]

40:44.810 --> 40:47.461
I SUPPOSED ONE
COULD CHOOSE THAT LIFE --

40:47.510 --> 40:53.005
HONEST WORK, COMMUNITY,
A LOVING FAMILY,

40:53.050 --> 40:56.417
AND NOT A WITCH IN SIGHT.
[ CHUCKLES ]

40:56.450 --> 40:59.840
MAYBE THERE'S HOPE FOR US YET.

40:59.890 --> 41:02.415
Increase: YOU!

41:02.460 --> 41:03.779
ALERT THE SELECTMEN.

41:03.820 --> 41:06.948
ANOTHER WITCH HAS BEEN REVEALED.
FOLLOW ME.

41:06.990 --> 41:08.457
John: OR MAYBE NOT.

41:09.330 --> 41:11.560
Increase: MARY SIBLEY!

41:15.400 --> 41:17.391
YOUR HUSBAND IS AWAKE.

41:23.640 --> 41:24.572
[ DOOR OPENS ]

41:26.750 --> 41:28.877
Mary: GEORGE IS AWAKE?

41:28.920 --> 41:30.319
HAS HE SPOKEN?

41:30.350 --> 41:32.784
Increase: HE IS RENDERED
INCAPABLE OF SPEECH.

41:32.820 --> 41:37.780
NEVERTHELESS, THE NAME OF HIS
TORMENTOR HAS BEEN DIVULGED.

41:37.820 --> 41:39.959
Mary: WHAT DOES THAT MEAN --

41:39.990 --> 41:41.423
"RENDERED UNABLE TO SPEAK"?

41:42.730 --> 41:44.869
Increase:
DO YOU RECOGNIZE THIS POTION?

41:44.900 --> 41:46.322
Mary: YES.

41:46.370 --> 41:48.065
IT'S A PHYSIC FOR PAIN.

41:48.100 --> 41:51.467
I GAVE IT TO ISAAC
TO GIVE TO MR. SIBLEY.

41:51.500 --> 41:54.469
Increase: A PHYSIC FOR PAIN?

41:54.510 --> 41:59.174
TELL ME, WOULD A PHYSIC FOR PAIN

41:59.210 --> 42:03.317
SEAL MR. SIBLEY'S MOUTH SHUT...

42:03.350 --> 42:05.443
WITH A GOLDEN WEB?

42:20.900 --> 42:23.039
Mary: A TONIC FOR PAIN.

42:23.070 --> 42:24.332
NOTHING MORE.

42:24.370 --> 42:27.430
Cotton:
MIGHT I SUGGEST, FATHER,

42:27.470 --> 42:30.701
THAT MRS. SIBLEY'S
TONIC IS JUST THAT,

42:30.740 --> 42:32.071
AND THE WORK OF THE WEB IS DUE,

42:32.110 --> 42:35.318
MORE LIKELY, TO THE REAL
WITCH'S SPIDER FAMILIAR.

42:40.390 --> 42:42.950
Increase: YES.

42:42.990 --> 42:45.424
IT'S A POSSIBILITY.
SEARCH THE HOUSE.

42:45.460 --> 42:47.678
Mercy: WAIT!

42:47.730 --> 42:50.221
I'M SORRY, SIR.

42:50.260 --> 42:52.228
DID YOU SAY A SPIDER?

42:52.270 --> 42:57.230
Cotton:
THE LEWIS CHILD, ONCE TORTURED
AND POSSESSED BY WITCHES.

42:57.270 --> 42:59.363
Increase: YET NOW
SHE LOOKS REMARKABLY WELL.

42:59.410 --> 43:02.436
Mercy: ALL DUE TO MRS. SIBLEY'S
KINDNESS.

43:02.480 --> 43:04.698
SHE SAVED MY LIFE.

43:04.750 --> 43:07.469
I WAS TORTURED AND TORMENTED,

43:07.510 --> 43:09.978
AT THE VERGE
OF BEGGING FOR DEATH,

43:10.020 --> 43:13.217
AND MARY SIBLEY
DELIVERED ME FROM EVIL.

43:13.250 --> 43:16.048
WHICH IS WHY
I HESITATE TO SAY --

43:16.090 --> 43:18.456
Increase: WHAT IS IT
YOU HAVE TO SAY, GIRL?

43:18.490 --> 43:19.889
Mercy: THE OTHER MORNING,

43:19.930 --> 43:24.299
WHEN MRS. SIBLEY WAS OUT
ON SHIPPING BUSINESS...

43:24.330 --> 43:25.592
Increase: YES?

43:25.630 --> 43:29.066
Mercy:
...I DID PASS TITUBA'S ROOM,

43:29.100 --> 43:32.433
AND SHE WAS DOING
THE STRANGEST THING.

43:32.470 --> 43:34.335
Cotton: TELL US, MERCY.
TELL US WHAT YOU SAW.

43:34.370 --> 43:36.930
Mercy:
SHE HELD A SPIDER TO HER NECK.

43:38.780 --> 43:40.577
Cotton: YES?

43:40.610 --> 43:41.975
YES?

43:42.020 --> 43:43.976
Mercy: SHE SEEMED TO FEED IT.

43:44.020 --> 43:45.647
[ ALL GASP ]

43:45.690 --> 43:48.511
Increase: YOU.

43:48.550 --> 43:50.188
COME HERE.

43:50.220 --> 43:52.154
[ CROWD CHATTERING ]

44:00.630 --> 44:04.930
I HEREBY ARREST YOU...

44:04.970 --> 44:07.029
ON THE CHARGE OF WITCHCRAFT.

44:07.070 --> 44:09.004
[ CROWD GASPS ]
GUARDS.

44:09.040 --> 44:11.031
-Man: YES, SIR.
-Man #2: AYE, SIR.

44:17.980 --> 44:20.210
Man: COME WITH US.

44:34.270 --> 44:37.330
-- Captions by VITAC --
